    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\Rightarrow d(AC, SM) = d(AC, (SMN)) = d(I, (SMN)) \\ (\\text{với } I = DN \\cap AC)\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      76,
      833,
      155,
      867
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "Ta có"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      79,
      892,
      1299,
      1103
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\begin{aligned} ID \\cap (SMN) = N \\Rightarrow \\frac{d(I, (SMN))}{d(D, (SMN))} &= \\frac{IN}{DN} = \\frac{1}{5} \\ (\\text{do } AN \\parallel CD \\Rightarrow \\frac{IN}{ID} = \\frac{AN}{CD} = \\frac{1}{4} \\Rightarrow \\frac{IN}{DN} = \\frac{1}{5}) \\\\ \\Rightarrow d(I, (SMN)) &= \\frac{1}{5} d(D, (SMN)). \\end{aligned}\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      76,
      1127,
      414,
      1164
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "Xét $\\triangle ADN$ và $\\triangle DCA$ có"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      79,
      1187,
      506,
      1554
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\begin{aligned} \\hat{D} &= \\hat{A} = 90^{\\circ} \\\\ \\frac{AN}{AD} &= \\frac{AD}{DC} = \\frac{1}{2} \\\\ \\Rightarrow \\triangle ADN &= \\triangle DCA \\ (c.g.c) \\\\ \\Rightarrow \\widehat{ADN} &= \\widehat{DCA} \\\\ \\Rightarrow DN \\perp AC \\Rightarrow MN \\perp (SDN). \\end{aligned}\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      76,
      1580,
      155,
      1615
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "Ta có"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      79,
      1639,
      747,
      1805
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\begin{cases} (SMN) \\perp (SDN) \\\\ (SMN) \\cap (SDN) = SN \\Rightarrow d(D, (SMN)) = DH \\\\ \\text{Trong } (SDN), DH \\perp SN \\end{cases}\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      79,
      1834,
      798,
      2017
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\begin{aligned} \\triangle SDN \\text{ vuông tại } D: \\quad \\frac{1}{DH^2} &= \\frac{1}{SD^2} + \\frac{1}{DN^2} \\Rightarrow DH = 5 \\\\ \\Rightarrow d(I, (SMN)) &= \\frac{1}{5} d(D, (SMN)) = 1. \\end{aligned}\n$$"
  },
